# __TITLE__

A book in progress, by __AUTHOR__.

## Status

Skeleton. The chapters compile and the design system works; prose has not yet been drafted.

## How to compile

```bash
pdflatex book.tex
biber book
pdflatex book.tex
pdflatex book.tex
```

The book uses `memoir` as its document class with a custom style at `style/__SLUG__.sty`. The style provides:

- Palatino body (`mathpazo`)
- Reclaimed Gov 2001 palette (charcoal, slate, ocean, forest, crimson, warmgray, lightbg)
- A `\voice{<name>}{<text>}` macro for named voices
- `\sidenote{}` for margin notes
- `idea` and `warn` callout environments

## Companion files

- `CLAUDE.md` — book-level rules for working with Claude on this project
- `decks/README.md` — pointers (not copies) to source decks
- `correspondence/` — letters and email threads
- `bibliography/__SLUG__.bib` — citation skeleton; run `/bibcheck` before chapter check-ins

## Public version

A free online version can be produced from this source via `tex4ht` or a Quarto pipeline once the print version is complete.
